skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Wondering what is going on in today's South Florida real estate market? I lighten and brighten my flash briefing up daily with entertaining tips for you if you are thinking of buying or selling a home in South Florida. Each day you can hear a homebuyer and a homeseller tip. Lets face it, buying or selling a home can be stressful...let me share some of my tips, techniques, resources, experiences and humor with you while you are pondering your next "move" ... get it LOL! 

Michele Bellisari is a Realtor with RE/Max Services and the founder of #SoooBoca Lifestyle & Media ...she blogs and vlogs in sunglasses, loves Instagram, live posts on FB and constantly shines the light on how fabulous Boca is and shares her life with her millennials. You never know when she will be "buzz' about Boca, the Palm Beaches, South Florida and Beyond. Want to get to know #SoooBoca better and get random pop up special offers and info then subscribe to our blog www.soooboca.com/subscribe. See you somewhere in #SoooBoca!
